Summary: one large glowing light and one red light behind it, but the red light was at a distance that it would not be airplane.
divs: Sighting DetailsWinnipeg, MB Canada, August 8 2013 23:15 Observed two lights, the leading light was solid white with the following light a dimmer solid red light. These 2 lights were at a altitude that a international jet would travel. but the distance between the two lights, which were consistantly the same distance apart, was much too large.
